OL,3,CTeachers and NHS staff to receive pay
OL,4,Crise, First Minister announces
OL,6,FFirst Minister Eluned Morgan has
OL,7,Fannounced pay awards for public sector
OL,8,Fworkers in Wales.
OL,10,FNHS staff and teachers will be among
OL,11,Fsome of the public sector workers to
OL,12,Freceive pay increases of between 5%
OL,13,Fand 6% in 2024-25.
OL,15,FAccording to the Welsh Government,
OL,16,Fthey have accepted the pay
OL,17,Frecommendations from independent pay
OL,18,Freview bodies in full.
OL,20,FTeachers will be entitled to a 5.5%
OL,21,Fpay award, as will certain NHS staff.
