OL,6,F"Plaid Cymru has consistently
OL,7,Fcampaigned for public sector workers
OL,8,Fto get fair pay for the invaluable
OL,9,Fwork they do for our country.
OL,11,F"We're clear that public sector
OL,12,Fworkers in Wales should not have to
OL,13,Fawait for announcements in England
OL,14,Fbefore receiving improved pay offers.
OL,15,FThat's why we urgently need a fair
OL,16,Ffunding model to end Wales' dependency
OL,17,Fon political decisions made over the
OL,18,Fborder.
